how to unify different computing devices?

devices could be gaming console. work station, personal computer, Iot devices. 
possible computing devices could be cpu, multicore cpus, gpu, fpga, other computing devices. 

how to map the computing code to computing devices effeiciently?
different computing devices have different charastics. 


